- Conclusion: The disk had previously been used in a Windows VM, so it must be reattached there to access the data.  
âœ… **Result:** Immich online and syncing photos automatically from mobile.  
ğŸ’¡ **Learning:** Learned about the limitations of ZFS import. Important to remember what system a disk was used in beforeâ€”donâ€™t try to force it into TrueNAS if it belongs in Windows.  

